  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/e69a0ad514fe9354d777bd0a3adc579d.poster.avif?t=1771917039\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/e69a0ad514fe9354d777bd0a3adc579d.webm?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/e69a0ad514fe9354d777bd0a3adc579d.mp4?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">You are inside an endless School but there is a way you can escape. Search in the hallways </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">of the school and find the changes within them to reach Room 14.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If you find anomalies, turn around! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If you think the room is normal continue to the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">To get to Room 14.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Room 14 is a small walking simulator inspired by the backrooms and liminal spaces.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/fccb25b9f07ca7eb6804d559613aed98.poster.avif?t=1771917039\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/fccb25b9f07ca7eb6804d559613aed98.webm?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/fccb25b9f07ca7eb6804d559613aed98.mp4?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/3300c3ee6d845139b65a5c8c07c8f0d5.poster.avif?t=1771917039\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/3300c3ee6d845139b65a5c8c07c8f0d5.webm?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/3300c3ee6d845139b65a5c8c07c8f0d5.mp4?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">- Endless Hotel -</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">- 7 Shaders -</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">- 30+ Anomalies -</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/108ee864077f41af1cf1ccf249c0dcf4.poster.avif?t=1771917039\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/108ee864077f41af1cf1ccf249c0dcf4.webm?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/108ee864077f41af1cf1ccf249c0dcf4.mp4?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/be6d5d543891774acda0d32923d33260.poster.avif?t=1771917039\" width=600 height=94 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/be6d5d543891774acda0d32923d33260.webm?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/be6d5d543891774acda0d32923d33260.mp4?t=1771917039\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This experience can last up to 15 - 60 minutes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">It can last longer if you playthrough the game with the different shaders and if find all of the anomalies.<br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Asset Credits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976500/extras/628be3bf708aa3b714ab74a36240af4d.avif?t=1771917039\" width=682 height=440 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
